      "updated": 1778058672279,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "PROXMOX — 6 BRIDGES RÉSEAU\n\nvmbr0 — WAN (bridge VMware → internet)\nvmbr1 — LAN Lyon VLAN-aware (5,10,30,40,110)\nvmbr2 — MGMT isolé (Bastion uniquement)\nvmbr3 — LAN Marseille VLAN-aware (50,60)\nvmbr4 — Quarantaine isolé (cul-de-sac)\nvmbr5 — Collecte logs (Wazuh eth1)\n\n11 VMs · ~15 GB RAM · 150 GB disque",
